ygData.msgSnippet: Wood Elves think the willowisps are souls, and they become reborn into willowisps. So your faction to to wood elves get worse when you kill them. (its a rumor)
ygData.messageBody:
Wood Elves think the willowisps are souls, and they become reborn into
